{
  "id": "adv_main_04_01_04",
  "title": "星空編1章4話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "お忙しいのにお呼び立てしてすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to call you when you're busy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それは構わないが……\nさっき送ってきたメッセージ、あれは本気なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's fine‚ but…\nMessage you just sent‚ are you serious?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "本気です\n次のライブバトルで『彼女達』と対戦させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm serious\nPlease‚ let me fight 'them' in the next live battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……どうして急にそんなことを？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Why did you suddenly think of that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "急に思いついた訳ちゃう\nこれは前から考えてたことなんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It wasn't something we just thought of\nThis is something we've been thinking about before",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリで敗退してから私達は\nずっと、強い相手との対戦を心のどこかで避けてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After losing NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚\nwe have been secretly avoiding matches against strong opponents",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、少し前に100連勝を賭けて\nランキング五位の強い相手と対戦することになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ we recently set a record of 100 consecutive wins\nWe faced a strong opponent ranked 5th…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに支えられて……\nファンの声から大事なことに気付かされて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We got help from {user}-san…\nWe realized something important from the voices of our fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "新しいことに挑戦して、持てる力を全て出し切って\n勝利して分かったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We realized it only after we challenged ourselves with something new\nand won with all our power",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達に必要なものは、勝ち星の数じゃない\n本当に必要なのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What we need now is not the number of wins\nWhat we really need is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 58.2225396793
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "強いライバルと全力で競い合い\n勝利を掴み取ることだったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Compete against strong rivals\nand achieve victory",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "うちらはランキング五位になりました\nこれより強い相手はもうBIG4しかおらへん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We got ranked 5th\nThe only stronger opponents are now the BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.800286498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "三人で話し合ったんです。BIG4とライブバトルを\nするなら、私達が戦いたい相手は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Three of talked about it. If we were to have a live battle with the BIG4‚\nthe opponent we would want to fight is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "かつてNEXT VENUSグランプリで\nトリエルが敗北した……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once at the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix\nTRINITYAiLE was defeated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6369274855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "私達が倒すつもりだったⅢXに勝って\nBIG4の座を掴み取った……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Took down the IIIX we were trying to take down first\nand taking the place of BIG4…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うちらが足踏みしている間に\nトリエルを飛び越えてトップに登り詰めた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While we were spinning in place‚\njumped over TRINITYAiLE and climbed to the top…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_big4-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 97.2638775507
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main_04_01_04_movie-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 97.2638775507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピース",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "BIG4と戦うのなら、私達は彼女達と戦いたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we fight the BIG4‚ we want to fight them",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "サニーピースに勝つことが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Winning Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達が前に進むために必要なことなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "is what we need to move forward",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……みんなの気持ちは分かった\nだが、それは今すぐじゃなくてもいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I understand what everyone is thinking\nBut‚ it doesn't have to be right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9999944051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピとトリエルが戦うのなら\nもっとふさわしい舞台があるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Sunny Peace and TRINITYAiLE were to fight‚\nthere must be a more suitable stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3333277385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "それは、VENUSグランプリのことを言うてはるん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you talking about VENUS Grand Prix?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.8071667352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリのエントリーが始まったのは知っています\nでも開催されるのは、まだ先の話ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We know the Grand Prix entries have started\nBut that will be open later‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3333323162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "私達はランキング五位になってから\nさらに高く羽ばたけるように練習を重ねてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we became ranked 5th\nWe continued to practice flying higher and higher",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.9666610718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 145.3030399004
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、ずっと機会を待ち続けているのに\nBIG4と戦うチャンスは一向に訪れない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ we've been waiting for our chance\nWe never had a chance to fight the BIG4…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4666610718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "このまま黙って待っていろと言うんですか？\n時がくるまで何もするなと言うんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you asking me to just wait quietly like this?\nDo nothing until the time comes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.4999944051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか……瑠依のこの気迫は、焦りの裏返しなんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see… Rui's momentum is to shake off her impatience）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.4405000685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（壁を乗り越えて、この勢いを止めたくないのに）\n（次々と他のグループが先にBIG4になって……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She wants to jump over the wall and keep this momentum‚）\n（but another group becomes the BIG4 first…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.2333277385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_04-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルはずっと伸び悩んでいました\nそれが今、ようやく前に進むきっかけを掴んだんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE couldn't move forward\nAnd now‚ we finally have the chance to move forward",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.0666610718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
